[🌟It’s Time for K-Culture🌟]
Pioneering illusion painting artist Dain Yoon (@designdain ) visited the “Only the Young: Experimental Art in Korea, 1960s-1970s” exhibition at the Guggenheim Museum (@guggenheim ).

Please find the “It’s Time for K-Culture” brochures at the Guggenheim Museum’s admission desk for more information. 

Video by Anthony A (@kidantvlogs ) 

#kccny #itstimeforkculture #ExperimentalArtInKorea

Waking up to see my face on the front page of CNN! I had a fun time chatting with @cnnstyle about my works, my creative process and my experience moving and living in another country. Thank you to Christy for bringing out my inner thoughts and feelings, and for the wonderful write-up. Link in bio 🗞️
365 pieces of my 2023. Succeeded taking a Polaroid every day for the past two years. Welcome 2024, happy new year! 🐉
